{"tid":1773660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12.8維園大遊行攻略","createTime":"2019-12-07T15:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T16:19:52.000Z","uid":179703,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6b4622fe3297707fee67bf21a46faed6908bdb2d","tid":1773660,"uid":179703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"其實點都好聽日班狗點都會派卧底搞事，之前發夢有高人指點，依家發開口夢。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和平重點：天橋</span><br />\n班狗每次都佔左制高點，跟住大家屌狗，停左就唔會郁，之後人多一亂，班鬼就擲天橋班狗，最後就清場.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hxDC0NQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhxDC0NQ.png&h=ecb0d8a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFRw5ew.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFRw5ew.png&h=524331ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢三條橋最易出事，灣仔站行人天橋，狗總天橋，同金鐘行車天橋</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解決方法：聽日記者，糾察，真橫額和理非，攝影既手足同唔想行咁遠既手足，請站爆呢三條橋既邊位，影相吹水又好</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要唔比班狗站到係到，唔好比到機會佢地既鬼擲野！咁就算出事，都係班狗理虧，我地真和平遊行</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非記住可屌狗，可屌狗，但一定要行住屌，唔好停低，大把手足接力屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對勇武派的話：真係打，戰場逼去紅星</span></span>"},{"pid":"ecb31cb9a8b8031a1ad4a0039ccb40760ce62065","tid":1773660,"uid":179703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b4622fe3297707fee67bf21a46faed6908bdb2d","tid":1773660,"uid":179703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"其實點都好聽日班狗點都會派卧底搞事，之前發夢有高人指點，依家發開口夢。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和平重點：天橋</span><br />\n班狗每次都佔左制高點，跟住大家屌狗，停左就唔會郁，之後人多一亂，班鬼就擲天橋班狗，最後就清場.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hxDC0NQ.